      • exportSelected

        public static void exportSelected​(java.io.File outputFile)
                           throws java.io.FileNotFoundException,
                                  java.io.IOException
        Method that, given a File object to write to, converts each HTML string from all selected reports to individual PDFs and merges all of them together.
        Parameters:
        outputFile - File object which is the destination of the PDF file.
        Throws:
        java.io.FileNotFoundException - when something is wrong with the filepath.
        java.io.IOException - when something goes wrong whilst writing to the filepath.
